          <li><b>Ideas</b>: Everyone has ideas on how to increase revenues or make the company more efficient.  Enter your idea and let your colleagues comment and vote on the best ideas.</li>
        </p>
        <p class="text-center-xs"><a href="#" class="btn btn-lg btn-default">Find out more</a></p>
